        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>No Tax Deductions for Workplace Harasser Buyouts Act</b></p> <p>This bill modifies the tax deduction for trade or business expenses to deny a deduction for payments made to any employee in connection with the termination of employment if a factor in the termination was sexual assault, sexual harassment, sexual misconduct, or workplace harassment based on race, color, national origin, religion, sex, disability, or other specified factors.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
